title: Have a giggle this Weekend with comedian Patrick Kielty
text:
Tweet 
Elsewhere, we get all wrapped up for winter as our girl Bozzers rounds up what to read, watch, eat and do when the dark nights draw in. 
Fashion icon Twiggy shows us how to turn over a new leaf with a load of autumn style ideas while home styles embraces all that's art deco. 
Spooky new drama Jekyll & Hyde is previewed on our TV pages, plus there are mentions for The Apprentice, Skins and the new James Bond. What do you think?
